questionText: Rate your experience. (1 = tyring, boring, etc.; 10 = very enjoyable)
Rate your patience level during the experiment. (1=impatient; 10=patient)
Did you experience any fatigue? (1 = no fatigue, 10 = a lot of fatigue)
What was your stress level during the experiment? (1=not stressed at all; 10=very stressed)
Did you notice any change in your performance throughout the experiment?
